nsistent elevational decline in non-native\nspecies richness. Non-native plants were also more abundant directly\nadjacent to road edges, suggesting that disturbed roadsides serve as a\nvector for invasions into mountains. From the upcoming analyses of time\nseries even more exciting results especially about range shifts can be\nexpected. Implementing the protocol in more mountain regions globally\nwould help to generate a more complete picture of how global change\nalters species distributions. This would inform conservation policy in\nmountain ecosystems, where some conservation policies remain poorly\nimplemented.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Haider, Sylvia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lembrechts, Jonas", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "McDougall, Keith", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Pauchard, Anibal", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Alexander, Jake M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Barros, Agustina", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Cavieres, Lohengrin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Rashid, Irfan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Rew, Lisa", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Aleksanyan, Alla", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sierra, Jos\u00e9 Arevalo", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Aschero, Valeria", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chisholm, Chelsea", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Clark, Vincent Ralph", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Clavel, Jan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Daehler, Curtis", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Dar, Pervaiz", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Dietz, Hansjoerg", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Dimarco, Romina", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Edwards, Peter", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Essl, Franz", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fuentes-Lillo, Eduardo", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Guisan, Antoine", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gwate, Onalenna", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hargreaves, Anna", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jakobs, Gabi", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jim\